author: Jean-Claude Wippler
title: JeeNode wireless microcontroller
description: The JeeNode is a low-cost combination of radio and microcontroller board. Think of the JeeNode as an Arduino + Xbee shield + Xbee, but smaller and less feature-full than the XBee. This is the through-hole kit, but the headers are pin-compatible with the JeeNode SMD, the JeeNode SMD, and the SMD Kit.
